name: Tasks-made-easy-beta
tagline: A manager for your life, this app will help manage your life with a simple UI that helps you keep track of your daily tasks.
body:
### Welcome to TasksMadeEasy.
This program will help you manage your daily life with a simple, modern, and beautiful UI that follows Google's Material Design Color schemes, combined with total reliability that will organize your day for you.

### Authors and Contributors
Created by Hudson Havenhill (@hudohudo) and Eric Qian (@eqian) for AP Computer Science. Development was further taken over by Hudson Havenhill (@hudohudo) to create new versions.
### Support or Contact
Email Hudson and havenhillhudson@gmail.com with bug reports and feature requests.
